ssets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T06:43:32.000Z","msg":"巴打我知唔係你，我講緊個所謂筆者啫"},{"pid":"b881649554c7bb13118bb223d3242dc9afd06355","tid":657454,"uid":159798,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T06:43:49.000Z","msg":"金馬倫去年批評《神奇女俠》時也說過。他指神奇女俠的形象不單不是進步，反而是倒退一步（Step Backwards）。他在《未來戰士》中塑造的莎拉康納（Sarah Connor）就比神奇女俠更獨立、自主、剛強得多。<br />\n<br />\n佢老喇，而家D女人唔係要剛強，係要有著數<br />\n即係想點就點，大撚晒，時而屈人非禮，時而貼埋大床"},{"pid":"ceaa39361588ad9c7c9f02e2ef1e6340d1b643d0","tid":657454,"uid":6242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T06:44:41.000Z","msg":"占飛 忽然文化<br />\n原來係忽然之間先睇到呢套戲<br />\n寫文前做下功課先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bc2730fa2603d7708a545c497722c2103edaf55","tid":657454,"uid":185749,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T06:45:40.000Z","msg":"自己唔睇開頭就屌人套戲冇開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n姐係條女唔肯同條仔玩前戲就話鳩條仔唔識做愛 冇做前戲就入戲肉<br />\n<br />\n都on99 死撚左佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e3d7f00d3fb8736d43188a21f81891c235d4683","tid":657454,"uid":34676,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"ceaa39361588ad9c7c9f02e2ef1e6340d1b643d0","tid":657454,"uid":6242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T06:44:41.000Z","msg":"占飛 忽然文化<br />\n原來係忽然之間先睇到呢套戲<br />\n寫文前做下功課先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T06:49:22.000Z","msg":"總係有啲廢老，唔知頭唔知路<br />\n見近排興咩就想入去睇下，出到嚟寫下影評貼近個熱度<br />\n奈何又唔做足功課，扮撚哂高尚有優越感<br />\n無啦啦噠句莎士比亞<br />\n<br />\n都唔知做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84d85cd73070a69286342ff9a3139bd9d1636791","tid":657454,"uid":6242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote"